---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";

const title = "Jasa Iklan Google untuk Bisnis yang Mau Closing";
const description =
  "Jasa iklan Google Ads yang fokus closing. Setup rapi. Budget aman. Bukan janji manis.";
---

<Base title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[780px] px-5 pb-20 pt-12 sm:pt-16">
    <section class="stagger">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-500">
        Jasa Iklan Google
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl">
        Jasa Iklan Google untuk Bisnis yang Mau Closing
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
        Fokus Google Ads. Setup rapi. Bukan coba coba. Bukan trial.
        Yang dicari itu closing.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <a
          class="rounded-full bg-slate-900 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white"
          href="https://wa.me/6282253888174"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          Konsultasi Gratis via WhatsApp
        </a>
        <a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600" href="/jasa-iklan-google/">
          Lihat halaman utama
        </a>
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-slate-900"></span>
          Fokus Google Ads saja.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-slate-900"></span>
          Setup rapi. Bukan trial.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-slate-900"></span>
          Cocok UMKM sampai bisnis serius.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 border-t border-slate-200 pt-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
        Kenapa iklan sering boncos
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
        <p>
          Banyak iklan boncos bukan karena produknya jelek. Masalahnya setup.
          Keyword terlalu lebar. Iklan tidak nyambung. Landing page jadi pajangan.
        </p>
        <p>
          Google Ads itu presisi. Kalau sinyalnya jelas hasilnya kelihatan.
          Kalau asal set budget ya kebakar.
        </p>
        <p>
          Baca lebih lengkap di
          <a class="underline" href="/jasa-iklan-google/">jasa iklan google</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 border-t border-slate-200 pt-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Layanan inti</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Jasa Iklan Google Search
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
            Fokus keyword niat tinggi. Cocok untuk bisnis yang mau closing cepat.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Jasa Iklan Google Display
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
            Untuk awareness dan retargeting. Tetap rapi dan terukur.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Jasa Iklan Google YouTube
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
            Buat produk yang butuh edukasi singkat. Intent tetap jadi fokus.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 border-t border-slate-200 pt-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">FAQ singkat</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
        <details class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Berapa budget minimal Google Ads
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Tergantung industri. Yang penting setup benar dulu.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Bisa fokus di Google Search saja
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Bisa. Banyak bisnis paling cepat closing dari Search.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Ada kontrak panjang
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-2">Tidak wajib. Kami fokus hasil.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-slate-500">
        Lihat FAQ lengkap di
        <a class="underline" href="/jasa-iklan-google/">jasa iklan google</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <footer class="mt-14 border-t border-slate-200 pt-8 text-sm text-slate-500">
      <p>WhatsApp: +62 822-5388-8174</p>
      <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a class="underline" href="/about/">Tentang</a>
        <a class="underline" href="/contact/">Kontak</a>
        <a class="underline" href="/jasa-iklan-google/">jasa iklan google</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Base>
